  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/645360/extras/4313c4ff180acdf46c073ff7bafa9cbd.webp?t=1650833005\" width=300 height=56 /></span><br><br>Cube XL is a hardcore infinite runner cube game. You are a cube moving in a plane with a ability to change the gravity. Try to get the highest score without hitting any block.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Infinite level<br></li><li>Addicting gameplay<br></li><li>Fun background music<br></li><li>Aaand.. CUBE!</li></ul>",
